HEADWORD: Tape deck
<hw>Tape deck</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>an electronic device
for recording and playing back sounds on magnetic tape; usually it needs
to be connected to an amplifier system for playback.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

